longBusinessSummary: Sleep Cycle AB (publ) engages in providing sleep tracking applications in Sweden. It develops sleep and health platforms. The company offers Sleep Cycle app, an application that provides sleep-related solutions. Sleep Cycle AB (publ) was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
